text: OMG. Can you guys imagine just how crazy GARNiDELiA's concert is? I attend their Anime Garden concert in Gardens By the Bay, Singapore on 18th of April with a friend. and HOLY SHIET. The mood in the garden instantly changes the moment Maria and Toku came out. It suddenly feels like you are in a pub. Their songs just makes you feel excited and their an urge to move your body along with the music. Now i understand how they become a hit group in a short time. if you haven't try to listen to their song or go to the concert, don't hesitate and just try to once. especially if they are free. I assure you that you will not regret it.
